    <body><p><seg rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
此度出崎仕候上ハ、御存<seg rend="superscript" rendition="sup">（知）</seg>の事件ニ候間、万一の御報知仕候時ハ、愚妻儀本国ニ送り返し可<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>申、然レバ国本より家僕及老婆壱人、御家まで参上仕候。其間愚妻おして尊家に御養置可<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>被<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>遣候よふ、万<seg facs="../../../gaiji/1-02/1-02-22.png" rend="gaiji" rendition="img" source="※(二の字点、1-2-22)" />御頼申上候。拝稽首。<lb />
<seg rend="jisage_2" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 2em">五月八日<seg rend="chitsuki_0" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 0em">龍馬</seg></seg>
<seg rend="jisage_3" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 3em">慎蔵様</seg>
<seg rend="jisage_6" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 6em">左右</seg>
<seg rend="jisage_2" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 2em">三吉慎蔵様<seg rend="chitsuki_0" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 0em">坂本龍馬</seg></seg>
<seg rend="jisage_7" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 7em">御直披</seg>
<seg rend="jisage_2" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 2em">五月八日出帆時ニ認而家ニ止ム。</seg>
<seg rend="jisage_4" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 4em">卯<seg rend="chitsuki_0" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 0em">（朱印）</seg></seg>
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</seg></p></body>
